|3 |    └─HASH DISTINCT            |        |1       |7           |
|4 |      └─HASH JOIN              |        |1       |7           |
|5 |        ├─HASH RIGHT ANTI JOIN |        |1       |5           |
|6 |        │ ├─SUBPLAN SCAN       |VIEW2   |1       |3           |
|7 |        │ │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |supplier|1       |3           |
|8 |        │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |partsupp|1       |3           |
|9 |        └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |part    |1       |3           |
===================================================================
